<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Us - I Reload Cell</title>
    <!-- Bootstrap CSS -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <style>
        /* Base styles */
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            min-height: 100vh; /* Set minimum height to 100% of viewport height */
        }


        header {
            background-color: #333;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between; /* Align items horizontally */
            align-items: center; /* Align items vertically */
        }


        header .logo h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 24px;
        }

        nav ul {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
            margin: 0;
        }

        nav ul li {
            display: inline;
            margin-right: 10px;
        }

        nav ul li a {
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        /* Hamburger menu styles */
        .menu-icon {
            display: none;
            font-size: 24px;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        /* Card styles */
        .card {
            background-color: #fff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 50px auto;
            max-width: 800px; /* Adjusted maximum width */
            text-align: center;
        }

        /* Footer styles */
        footer {
            background-color: #333;
            color: #fff;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px 0;
            width: 100%;
            margin-top: auto; /* Set margin-top to auto to push footer to the bottom */
        }

        /* Media query for mobile */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            nav ul {
                display: none;
            }

            .menu-icon {
                display: block;
                margin-right: 10px;
            }

            .menu-items {
                display: none;
                text-align: left;
            }

            .menu-items.active {
                display: block;
            }

            header .logo {
                display: none; /* Hide logo on mobile */
            }

            .card {
                margin: 50px auto;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <div class="logo">
            <h1>I Reload Cell</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="menu-icon" onclick="toggleMenu()">â˜°</div>
        <nav>
            <ul class="menu-items" id="menuItems">
                <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
                <li><a href="/login">Masuk</a></li>
                <li><a href="/register">Daftar</a></li>
                <li><a href="/about">About</a></li>
                <li><a href="/contact">Contact</a></li>
            </ul>
        </nav>
    </header>
    <main>
        <div class="card">
            <h1>About Us</h1>
            <p>I Reload Cell adalah platform untuk melakukan penukaran point dari pembelian pulsa, listrik, top up e-wallet, top up driver saldo, top up game, serta melakukan transaksi di toko offline kami. Dapatkan point dari setiap transaksi dan tukarkan pointnya untuk berbagai keuntungan!</p>
        </div>
    </main>
    <footer class="fixed-bottom">
        <p>&copy; 2024 I Reload Cell. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>
    <script>
        function toggleMenu() {
            var menuItems = document.getElementById("menuItems");
            menuItems.classList.toggle("active");
        }
    </script>
</body>
</html>
